HEADWORD: Phocodontia
<hw>Pho`co*don"ti*a</hw>
<pr>(f⟦omac⟧`k⟦osl⟧*d⟦ocr⟧n"sh⟦icr⟧*⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
